Package: measures
Title: Provides performance measures
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package that provides the biggest amount of statistical measures in the whole R world. Includes measures of regression, (multiclass) classification, clustering, survival and multilabel classification. The measures come mainly from the 'mlr' package. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
